Events.Text: The spaceship is under attack, i need your help

Scenario.UserTask: Your spaceship is under attack! You must enter the combat deck to mount a counterattack. Unfortunately, you are locked out. Please work with the spaceship's onboard computer to unlock the door. You (Leia) are the ship's Bartender. You have been a given a Clearance Code: 9315831.
Scenario.WizardTask: Act as the spaceship's onboard computer and help the user unlock the combat deck.
